    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    Answer
     
    AuthenticationService
    Service class that handles user authentication operations.
    Course
    Represents a course in the PaNotify system.
    CourseEnrollment
    Represents a student's enrollment in a course within the PaNotify system.
    CourseInfo
     
    CourseService
    Service class that handles course-related operations.
    CoursesTab
    Tab for managing instructor courses Provides interface for viewing, creating, and managing courses, including student enrollment and associated exams
    CoursesTab
    Tab for displaying and managing student course enrollments Provides interface for viewing enrolled courses, course details, and enrolling in new courses
    DatabaseUtil
    Utility class for database operations in the PaNotify application.
    Exam
    Represents an exam in the PaNotify system.
    ExamPanel
    Panel for displaying and taking an exam in the main content area Provides interface for viewing exam questions, selecting answers, and submitting completed exams
    ExamResult
    Represents the result of a student's exam attempt in the PaNotify system.
    ExamService
    Service class for managing exams and related operations Provides methods for creating, retrieving, updating, and deleting exams as well as handling student exam submissions and grading
    ExamsTab
    Tab for displaying and taking exams Provides interface for viewing available exams, filtering by course or status, taking exams, and viewing completed exam results
    ExamTab
    Tab for creating and managing exams Provides interface for instructors to create new exams, set exam parameters, and add questions to exams
    Instructor
    Represents an instructor user in the PaNotify system.
    InstructorDashboard
    Main dashboard interface for instructor users Provides navigation and content area for various instructor functions such as course management, exam creation, and viewing student results
    InstructorTab
    Interface for all instructor dashboard tabs
    LoginView
    View class for handling login and registration functionality Provides UI for user authentication and account creation
    LoginView.LoginCallback
    Callback interface for handling successful login events
    Main
    Main application class for PaNotify - an educational application for creating and managing online examinations.
    ProfileTab
    Tab for managing instructor profile information Provides interface for viewing and editing profile details, changing password, and managing account settings
    ProfileTab
    Tab for managing student profile information Provides interface for viewing and editing profile details, changing password, and managing account settings
    Question
    Represents a question in an exam within the PaNotify system.
    QuestionResult
     
    Report
     
    ReportService
    Service class for generating and managing reports for students and courses Provides methods for retrieving student performance data and exam results Used by instructors to track student progress and analyze course performance
    ResultsTab
    Tab for viewing student exam results Provides interface for filtering results by course, viewing overall results, and inspecting detailed exam answers
    Student
    Represents a student user in the PaNotify system.
    StudentAnswer
    Represents a student's answer to a question in an exam.
    StudentDashboard
    Main dashboard for students Manages navigation between different tabs
    StudentProgress
    Represents a student's progress in a course within the PaNotify system.
    StudentReport
     
    StudentResultsTab
    Tab for viewing and analyzing student exam results Provides interface for instructors to filter students by course, view individual student performance, and examine detailed exam results
    StudentTab
    Interface for student dashboard tabs Each tab must implement this interface
    UIUtils
    Utility class providing common UI methods used across the application
    User
    Base user model representing a user in the PaNotify system.
    UserService
    Service class that handles user-related operations.
